page.title: 02BRACEBRIDGE
page.content: Site of original school(Bracebride now Manor Leas)is a car- park next to Gatehouse Pub.Bracebridge area has a lot of shops.Here are some of the shops. Post Office,Newsagents,Video,DIY, Fish & Chips,Chinese takeaway,Pet shop, Aquarium,Fishing shop, 2 Betting shops,2 hairdressers,Sweet shops and Cakes and pastries. {OTHER THINGS IN BRACEBRIDGE. Play area for children,Library,Council offices, Private Nursing Home,3 Garages, Youth Club Centre,Infants School, Garage with servicing,Doctors' surgery, Dentist surgery,Private sports club ground,Church,Chapel, Restaurant, Petrol filling station,Bus shelter and a Bank.
